## Deployment

### Standard Deploy (Staging)
```bash
make deploy-staging
# or
git push origin main  # Auto-deploys via CI/CD
```

### Production Deploy
```bash
# Requires manual approval in GitHub Actions
# 1. Merge to main
# 2. CI pipeline builds, tests, scans
# 3. Auto-deploys to staging
# 4. Approve production deployment in GitHub
make deploy-prod
```

### Rollback
```bash
# Option 1: Revert the commit
git revert HEAD
git push origin main

# Option 2: Deploy previous image
# {rollback_command}

# Option 3: Kubernetes rollback
kubectl rollout undo deployment/{deployment_name} -n {namespace}
```

### Verify Deployment
```bash
# Health check
curl -s https://{domain}/health | jq .

# Readiness check
curl -s https://{domain}/ready | jq .

# Check logs
{logs_command}

# Check metrics
{metrics_command}
```

