## Monitoring

### Key Dashboards
- **Service Health**: {health_dashboard_url}
- **Error Tracking**: {error_tracking_url}
- **Infrastructure**: {infra_dashboard_url}

### Key Metrics
| Metric | Warning | Critical | Action |
|--------|---------|----------|--------|
| Error rate | > 0.5% | > 1% | Check logs, consider rollback |
| p99 latency | > {threshold}ms | > {critical_threshold}ms | Check DB, cache, dependencies |
| CPU usage | > 70% | > 90% | Scale up, investigate hotspots |
| Memory usage | > 80% | > 95% | Scale up, check for leaks |
| Disk usage | > 70% | > 90% | Clean logs, expand volume |

